---
import PageLayout from '../layouts/PageLayout.astro';
import PaperCard from '../components/PaperCard.astro';
import { getCollection } from 'astro:content';

const papers = (await getCollection('papers')).sort((a, b) => b.data.year - a.data.year);
---

<PageLayout title="Papers — Yumin Cao" pageTitle="Papers" pageTitleZh="论文">
  <p class="papers-intro lang-en">
    My research background is in transportation and urban computing — using ML to understand
    how people and goods flow through cities. These days I apply that systems-thinking foundation
    to AI agent architectures at Xiaomi. The papers below are from the earlier chapter.
  </p>
  <p class="papers-intro lang-zh">
    我的研究背景是交通与城市计算——用机器学习理解人和货物如何在城市中流动。
    如今我将这些系统性思维应用于小米的 AI Agent 架构。以下论文来自更早的研究阶段。
  </p>
  <div class="papers-list stagger">
    {papers.map(paper => (
      <PaperCard
        title={paper.data.title}
        authors={paper.data.authors}
        venue={paper.data.venue}
        year={paper.data.year}
        abstract={paper.data.abstract}
        links={paper.data.links}
      />
    ))}
  </div>
</PageLayout>

<style>
  .papers-intro {
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 640px;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  .papers-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 16px;
  }
</style>
